<p>
    While the Ratchet &amp; Clank logo has gone through some changes over the years, we were quite excited at the idea of having a custom font over at Ratchet-Galaxy. Clank93 was the original author of this font, and I cleaned it up a bit, adding upright letters, when I was designing the third version of the site. Below you can test it, see its available characters, and find where to download it!
</p>

